{"id":3144,"content":"<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【求实篇】<BR>1976年，华国锋和叶剑英怎样联手的．．．．．熊&nbsp; 蕾<BR>听华国锋谈几件大事．．．．．．．．．．张根生遗稿</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【亲历记】<BR>关于三峡的一场“御前辩论”．．．．．．．．韩&nbsp; 磊<BR>我的右倾罪：青海农村调查．．．．．．．．．王志敏<BR>绕航黑瞎子岛．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．吴广权</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【一家言】<BR>我看党与国家和人民的关系．．．．．．．．．应克复<BR>怎样选择突破口．．．．．．．．．．．．．．辛&nbsp; 宇</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【春秋笔】<BR>一篇更重要更全面的“窑洞对”<BR>——毛泽东答路透社记者甘贝尔问．．．．．．阎长贵<BR>共和国历史上的柯庆施．．．．．．．．．．．方海兴<BR>通渭问题——“大跃进”五十周年祭．．．．．杨继绳<BR>中国对阿尔巴尼亚的援助．．．．．．．．．．王洪起</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【冶方杯征文】<BR>1984年胡耀邦中苏边境行．．．．．．．．．．张持坚<BR>一项改革建议的提出和采纳．．．．．．．．．陈&nbsp; 力</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【怀人篇】<BR>我要说话——纪念母亲郑德芳．．．．．．．．蒋燕燕</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【品书斋】<BR>回忆父亲胡耀邦对我的教诲<BR>——从一封家信谈起．．．．．．．．．．．．胡德平</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【古今谈】<BR>“万岁”故事．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．雷&nbsp; 颐</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【海外事】<BR>“布拉格之春”四十周年祭（上篇）．．．．．赵启强</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\">【编读窗】<BR>读者来信．．．．．．．．．．．．．于俊沂&nbsp; 吴&nbsp; 镕</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10.5pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><BR></SPAN>&nbsp;</P>","title":"2008年第10期内容预告","time":1221761681999}